{"tid":281165,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[玩具撚又害人]【色魔落網】中學一齊打籃球 同學爆料：有時陰沉啲！","createTime":"2017-06-12T13:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T04:03:12.000Z","uid":21255,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10ebf14de9c78131afab7a57d500150139409302","tid":281165,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"【15：43更新】新增影片<br />\n屯門寶田邨發生令人髮指的強姦案(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2r8AFq3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2r8AFq3&d=oApwOix428vnKSn3%2BW8N7xxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=fea37231\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2r8AFq3</a>)，涉案男子仍被扣留調查。據知情人士透露，被捕男子6年前亦因在屯門區尾隨獨行女子返家，劫財劫色，他被捕後判囚6年半，早前才刑滿出獄，豈料又涉強姦案被捕。疑犯一名中學同學，對他屢次涉犯風化案感到可惜，有女同學更直言，日後如在街上撞見他，會兜路走。<br />\n<br />\n今次案中的被捕疑犯「阿文」，28歲。據其相熟的同學爆料稱，阿文中學時成績一般，「以前一齊打籃球，都好friend，佢主要打三分」、「冇咁變態，有時陰沉啲。」該同學指出，阿文常向朋友稱：「佢鐘意大波女㗎！」，但萬料不到，他於2011年會犯下非禮及搶劫罪(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2rlFdbT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rlFdbT&d=oApwOix428vnKSn3%2BW8N7xxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=16a55c78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2rlFdbT</a>)。<br />\n根據資料，當時22歲的阿文，涉嫌在屯門區內先後尾隨兩名女子返家，其中一名女事主更被推往後樓梯，被人以刀指頸搶走手機，有人更迫令她口交，女事主復遭在臉上射精及以精液塗臉，阿文事後被捕判監禁6年半。<br />\n阿文的舊同學稱，約半年前已在屯門區內多次撞見阿文，估計他剛出獄，「喺輕鐵站都見過幾次，佢主動話約出嚟食嘢，見佢個樣冇變，都係著短衫短褲波鞋look。」阿文的舊同學又說，一班女生談到如阿文今次再判監，日後出獄，「佢哋話撞見都會兜路走，但我就唔會，希望佢得到適當治療，唔好再犯事。」<br />\n<br />\n走啦玩具撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfd6abfea131ce386afaeaf45479c432973810c","tid":281165,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T14:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620426368c4eb10a7a85a8b2d9394c19ec76dce7","tid":281165,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T14:46:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47bff8c6c71d0edfc66c7817650b0cc51611afc8","tid":281165,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T14:48:09.000Z","msg":"樓主今次講得岩"},{"pid":"580dfab63da929231b93e1b516d422e8dabcaaab","tid":281165,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T14:48:24.000Z","msg":"見佢個樣冇變，都係著短衫短褲波鞋look<br />\n<br />\n30歲人仲短衫短褲波鞋係咪已經會比人標籤?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67437c8d03345bcbe17a690fd23795bfcb5a8c82","tid":281165,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:03:22.000Z","msg":"玩具撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e78097a441c418252b04adbfa5ce57cf8fde749","tid":281165,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:47:10.000Z","msg":"玩具撚殘害人世 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7461e23ecba84208ec901eb50386462808d9711a","tid":281165,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T04:00:33.000Z","msg":"害錯sor9"},{"pid":"609558ca7e629af776199a1009ad83e0bae7e879","tid":281165,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T04:03:12.000Z","msg":"黑人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}